Package cross.datastructures.workflow

Interface Summary
IWorkflow Workflow models a sequence of produced IWorkflowResults, which usually are files created by IWorkflowElement objects.
IWorkflowElement A Workflow element.
IWorkflowFileResult  
IWorkflowProgressResult  
IWorkflowResult A result of a IWorkflowElement, linking to a created file or immediate resources (e.g. statistics).
 

Class Summary
DefaultWorkflow A default implementation of IWorkflow.
DefaultWorkflowProgressResult To avoid numerous instances of this object, you should only instantiate it once per IWorkflowElement and then update its state, before dispatching it with an event.
DefaultWorkflowResult Default implementation of an IWorkflowResult.
WorkflowFactory Factory for the creation of IWorkflow instances.
